# Web3Forms access key — powers the enquiry form (components/Enquire.tsx).
# Get one free at https://web3forms.com (enter captain@myhana.com; they email you the key).
# The form submits directly from the browser to Web3Forms, so this key is public by
# design (email/domain-bound, not a secret) — hence the NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix.
# Set this in .env.local for local dev, AND in the Vercel project's Environment Variables for production.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=your-web3forms-access-key-here
